description: Russia launched a sweeping attack on Ukraine which killed one person, injured at least 24 others, and damaged infrastructure and residential buildings, authorities said on Saturday. Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky reported impacts on 14 regions by ...

description: A USAID inspector general’s report released Thursday lists Mathieu Zahiu as one of the agency’s current top employees, even though the IG told a D.C. judge last year that it had seized Zahui’s phone and found evidence that he took secret payments from a company to which he steered suspicious contracts.
